| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1329 — Recovery Inhibition (babuk2)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 53fe025d-e8e7-5d42-870f-e47f4d2ff532"
